OL,3,CIndia swelters in record-breaking 50C
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FPeople were struggling in the blazing
OL,7,Fheat in India as the country has been
OL,8,Fstruck by a record-breaking heatwave
OL,10,FNorthern India is experiencing a
OL,11,Frecord-breaking heatwave, with
OL,12,Ftemperatures soaring above 50.5C in
OL,13,Fsome places.
OL,15,FDelhi recorded its highest ever
OL,16,Ftemperature of 49.9 degrees on
OL,17,FTuesday, surpassing a previous record
OL,18,Fof 49.2C in May 2022.
