OL,3,CIndia swelters in record-breaking 50C
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FThe oppressive heat has forced
OL,7,Fauthorities in the capital to impose
OL,8,Fwater rationing, with some areas
OL,9,Fstruggling to access water, and others
OL,10,Fleft with none at all.
OL,12,FElsewhere, the temperature in the city
OL,13,Fof Churu in the state of Rajasthan
OL,14,Fclimbed to 50.5C. Sirsa, a city in the
OL,15,Fstate of Haryana, saw thermometers
OL,16,Freach 50.3C, Indian authorities said.
