OL,3,CIndia swelters in record-breaking 50C
OL,4,Cheatwave
OL,6,FOne study found that heatwaves have
OL,7,Fkilled more than 24,000 people in the
OL,8,Fcountry since 1992.
OL,10,FThe increase in heat events in coming
OL,11,Fyears could threaten India's
OL,12,Fdevelopment, and risk reversing its
OL,13,Fprogress on poverty alleviation,
OL,14,Fhealth and economic growth,
OL,15,Fresearchers said.
